Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Prologue}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:20.98,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:51.03,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:11:59.03,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:30.08,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:00.04,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:04.02,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You were late today, Ebata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.89,Default,Ebata,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:08.53,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It's fine. But I must ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:10.57,Default,Ebata,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.07,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Whatever makes you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.06,0:00:17.78,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,972)}Yes, all five are working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:18.87,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:22.04,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Then I expect good things from their finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:24.29,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,May I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:27.33,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I have a bit of a selfish request.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.05,Italics,Dad,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:33.30,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'd like to quit tutoring as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:38.93,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you aware that Nino and Itsuki\Ngot in a fight and ran away from home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:41.18,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I never heard about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:43.10,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Have they resolved their issues?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:43.93,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:45.56,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:46.40,Italics,Dad,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:47.69,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:51.48,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Aren't you curious about \Nwhy they got in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:56.57,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't you care to know what they're thinking or what's bothering them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:00.83,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, I shouldn't talk like that to my employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:03.20,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh, wait, I'm quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:06.21,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why don't you try acting \Nlike a father like once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.21,0:01:07.41,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:13.55,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}... You've gone and done it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:15.21,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:19.34,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I won't give my daughters to a man like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:01.40,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Thank you, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:03.91,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'd always gotten allowances until last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:07.45,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I should have stayed home to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.66,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,"Good fortune"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.16,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.46,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.58,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I don't need my fortune told\Nto know how my year's going to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:18.92,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Ever since I met those girls,\NI've always had...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:20.59,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,the worst luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:31.81,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san} and Raiha{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.36,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} always around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.82,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop by our place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:37.82,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Nah, we'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.82,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.70,Italics,TV,0,0,0,,{\an8}I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.79,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,They kissed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.58,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's so romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.25,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why did you even invite us over?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:56.09,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Come on, it's the new year. Let's relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:59.71,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.30,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I made a New Year's meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:02.17,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:08.47,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.68,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Raiha{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:11.73,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.85,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I think I had the wrong idea about you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:18.82,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I'd heard your family was really rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:22.19,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,O-Oh, well, things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.61,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Sorry we don't really have much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:28.24,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We have to return the kimonos \Nto our landlord, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:31.79,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Anyway, you can make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.62,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:35.50,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you guys sure you're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.50,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.71,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Why are you sitting over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.88,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Isn't it cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.51,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Get in the kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:45.76,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Okay, Raiha, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.51,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.89,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'll give you a massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.26,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.68,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,No, I'm not really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:56.85,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,No fair, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.44,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,First come, first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.65,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I get his arms, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.28,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.69,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'd like to massage his legs, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.41,Italics,Raiha,0,0,0,,{*}Brother{*Onii-chan}'s popular all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:16.21,Italics,Raiha,0,0,0,,Mom, spring has come early for {*}Big Brother{*Onii-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.50,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What are you guys plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.17,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Urp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.63,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.63,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,We're just thanking you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.67,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.59,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You always work so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.93,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Something's really fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:31.14,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Please have some of my food, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.43,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,Way too fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.89,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Let's play the face matching game\N to get into the party mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:38.15,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,We made a quintuplets version!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.56,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,That's way too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.02,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.40,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,There's something we'd like to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.57,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's too early for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:48.20,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Why don't we all go to the other room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:52.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What are they scheming?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:55.87,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it bothers him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.59,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:05.71,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,We're asking him to continue \Nteaching us without pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.59,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I want to do something for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.97,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,And I don't want to depend on Father,\N if we can avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:17.47,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,But what is there that we could do for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.77,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Th-That's inappropriate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.23,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You were thinking the same thing,\N weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:30.61,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I can't imagine that'd make Futaro{**-kun} happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:33.24,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Who knows? He's a guy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:36.00,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You're an actress, aren't you? \NYou could give him a peck on the cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:39.00,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Wh-What exactly do you think actresses do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.50,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,B-But I mean, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.38,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,What about you, Miku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.50,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:48.76,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,And Futaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.68,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:51.26,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Smooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.76,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.01,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You've really led me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.72,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You can't stop me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.85,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,N-No, Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.35,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.40,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Wait, don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.86,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.32,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.53,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,What are you all talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.53,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Why not just do something \Nnormal and cook for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.99,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,You're good at cooking, Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Make him some snacks or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.37,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.63,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I was finally getting over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:27.13,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Why don't we just go tell him\Nwhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:28.96,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:30.84,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.47,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:33.93,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.05,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.52,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,This is Ichika's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.52,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.52,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.94,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You guys are playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.61,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,We changed the rules, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.70,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yotsuba, what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.95,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:58.62,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san}, you have cream on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.67,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,{*}B-Brother{*O-Onii-chan}! Yotsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:08.84,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Let's just call that peck on the cheek\Na payment for your tutoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.42,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that from Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.84,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,She caught me off-guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.43,Italics,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.55,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Payment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:17.31,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:22.85,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We aren't in any position to \Ncompensate you fairly right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.81,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh, you could have said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.19,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm just doing it because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.32,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't worry about paying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.57,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:35.57,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You can just give me a cut \Nwhen you make it big.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:40.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But I want it in writing! Five thousand yen\Nper person per day of tutoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.79,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,And I {\i1}will{\i0} collect, right down to the last yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:44.58,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Right, that's how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.29,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,And all five of you are here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.96,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's get cracking on the winter homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Winter homework, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.47,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.10,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:09:01.22,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We've all done our homework already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.73,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:07.02,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Well, let's just make it a \Nregular study session, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:07.98,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,{*}Big Brother{*Onii-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:10.44,Default,Raiha,0,0,0,,I'm going to go home\Nso I don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:11.78,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:12.99,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:18.37,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Futaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.70,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Can you help me with this bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.62,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:25.83,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,"Provide examples of words ending with -ish"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.71,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,-ish is a suffix that means "approximately,"\Nor kind of. So you have "pinkish"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:35.05,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,"Bookish," "thickish"...\NThere's also peckish, but that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.59,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:38.93,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.22,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.64,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Hey, Ichika, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:45.98,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.48,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm not... sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.77,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yeah, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.07,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.07,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Let her sleep for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:57.53,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Ichika's been working even more than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.74,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,She is paying our bills and expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:05.41,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Ichika\N that we get to have you here to teach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:09.54,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But what's the point\Nif she can't focus on studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.54,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hey, wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.17,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:13.92,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Why don't we work, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.64,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Do you have any work experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:21.22,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I-I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.60,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Will you have time to both study and work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.22,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,All of you are struggling to even pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:31.44,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'll work as a tutor, like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.82,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'll teach as I study.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.24,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,That way, I can improve \Nmy academics, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.82,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,It's two birds with one stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.20,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.95,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'd feel sorry for your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:45.33,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,How about working at a supermarket, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.66,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You'd be fired instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.37,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I want to try working at a maid café.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.87,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You might be surprisingly popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:52.09,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Permission denied!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.46,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You'd probably be \Na dominatrix, right, Nino?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.21,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.71,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Nino would work in food service, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.26,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,If I had to choose, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:04.85,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's always been your dream \Nto open your own shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,First I've heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:10.39,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's just a silly idea I had as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.86,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Don't take it too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.65,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I know a good cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:17.86,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Mille-feuille.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:18.99,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Eclairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.07,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Mont Blanc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:22.03,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Merci beaucoup.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.82,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:29.00,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I've worked several jobs so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but they all took some commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:33.75,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.17,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Now's the time to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.01,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Futaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:47.43,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Ichika! Please stop\N taking your clothes off in your sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.97,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Look away! Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.27,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.27,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I underestimated this job.
Comment: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.49,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1051,1)\fs8\shad0\fax-.1\c&H2E1D15&\3c&HDBDBDB&\frz346.3\pos(318.667,154.667)}Minimum one shift per week! Teach in any subject you're comfortable
Comment: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.49,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1051,1)\fs8\shad0\fax-.1\c&H2E1D15&\3c&HDBDBDB&\pos(283.333,248.666)\frz345}Fun home tutoring (Minimum two days per week,\None shift each!) No experience needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:10.54,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.33,Italics,Dad,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Itsuki{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.04,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.92,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Well? What do you think of my pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.76,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's just like yours, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.55,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Give me a raise, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.84,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Give it a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:30.56,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's underdone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.52,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be talking trash about Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.44,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll be a while\N before I can let you in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.07,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.98,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}, you can leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.03,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.57,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you firing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:47.28,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,We're closing at noon today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:50.99,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,We're renting the shop out\Nfor a movie shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.33,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You could have told me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.08,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:58.50,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Looking forward to working with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.50,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,If the movie takes off,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the fans will be coming in \Ndroves to visit the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:10.47,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,We'll have a pick with our business name\Nin the cakes that will be on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.85,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I wish I had his insatiable hunger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:15.31,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,That looks so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:17.52,Default,Person B,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.11,Default,Boss,0,0,0,,H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:20.90,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:27.12,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Thank you for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:32.45,Default,Director,0,0,0,,Scene 37-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:33.37,Default,Director,0,0,0,,Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:39.38,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to try this cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:43.13,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Now's not the time, Tamako!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:45.92,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.01,Default,Person B,0,0,0,,That's the cursed reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.01,Default,Person C,0,0,0,,They say if you get one, you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:55.77,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm too dumb to know\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:59.56,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Let's just have some cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.45,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What, Tamako{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.78,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Futaro{**-kun},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,would you mind not watching? \NIt's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.54,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why would you take up embarrassing work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:17.21,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm trying not to tell the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but we're running out of savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:23.84,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I mean, it turns out food and power\Nis a lot more expensive than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:27.80,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,So I decided to accept any work I can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:31.30,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I have to be strong for the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.47,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,So don't try to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.97,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm not going to dismiss your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:41.56,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,And I'm grateful to you for giving me\Nan opportunity to continue tutoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:45.48,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you could do better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:49.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Isn't this job still pretty unprofitable\Nfor how much it ties you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:54.33,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Nakano{*Nakano-san}, we're ready to start rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.08,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:03.09,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.38,Default,Director,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.88,Default,Director,0,0,0,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:08.80,Default,Director,0,0,0,,That one was good,\N but why don't we try another take?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:09.84,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:14.35,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,I wish the others could see her\Nbeing so ditzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:18.48,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,I hope you don't mind us using \Nthis pie for one more take.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.35,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:23.52,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,The pick's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:27.74,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's the dud that I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:29.99,Default,Director,0,0,0,,Ready! Action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:39.37,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.04,Default,Director,0,0,0,,Nice! That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.13,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You got Problem 5 wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:55.05,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.14,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You don't have anything to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:00.89,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,These things are only cool\Nwhen done in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.06,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you done with your script?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.65,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.48,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I memorized the whole thing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:09.61,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why can't you use that skill for studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:14.99,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,The curse kills me in the first part,\Nso I don't have that many lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.91,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You die a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:18.83,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:20.79,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Is the cake here all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:23.50,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,If I'm being kind, it was unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.75,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,If I'm being brutal,\N it was like Miku's home cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:28.17,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:30.34,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But you saved my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.67,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,That was an impressive lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:33.09,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.30,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,It's called {\i1}acting{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:39.43,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's true that you surprised me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:42.31,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I mean, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:45.65,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Y-You're kind of growing into \Nyour job as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:47.48,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,She's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:49.02,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:52.32,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,She almost had me saying \Nsomething smug to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:57.57,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Man, I'm amazed you can hide your\Nembarrassment in front of so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:01.08,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I really wish the others could see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:04.20,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Good work, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:10.34,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,I hate that I'm even acting\Nin this moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:13.63,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,Now I really am lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:20.43,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,But I couldn't let him see my face right now.
Comment: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:25.98,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H554CB8&\b1\3c&HECEDEF&\shad0}Hikarihime\N{\c&H2E2F31&}Delicious Rice\NFirst-class
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:27.48,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,So heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.65,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Stay calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:32.61,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Remember your mechanics!\N The most efficient way of carrying this load is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.11,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.74,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'll carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.62,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Hurry up, you bag handlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.37,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.61,0:17:45.16,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why'd you call me out at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.12,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,They're having a sale today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.50,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,And you should be able\Nto carry that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.46,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} carry it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.63,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.63,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Miku asked me to buy these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.76,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,She's eating all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.76,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You're pretty dense for \Nsomeone who's so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.52,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,It's so early, too. It's only January.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.39,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.27,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Wait, Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:09.36,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Can you hold this for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.86,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.28,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.28,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.16,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Sorry, Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:23.41,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.00,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,Something's weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:35.67,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,Maybe I haven't gotten over Kintaro{**-kun} yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:37.97,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.68,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:41.34,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:46.47,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,There's no way this guy's my prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:49.23,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.27,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:52.48,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Nino, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.70,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.36,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Bring us every kind of sandwich you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:00.99,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.45,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.66,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You don't want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:08.46,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'll take them. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.46,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:12.58,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You're amenable and quick \Nto understand, Itsuki{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:18.22,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I believe that's what is meant\Nwhen one is called "intelligent."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:22.34,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I knew it. It's Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:24.01,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Why is he with Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.26,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,That was definitely him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:29.52,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,That was him at the hospital back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:33.48,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,That man is their father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.98,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Now, Itsuki{**-kun}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:39.57,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'll turn a blind eye to the mistake\Nyou girls have made.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.95,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Come back home with the others immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.62,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Inform all of your sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.12,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Does that include him as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:50.75,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You mean Uesugi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:53.66,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,This is a family matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:55.75,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He's an outsider in every sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:58.38,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,And, to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.76,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:04.76,Italics,Itsuki,0,0,0,,That's so childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.31,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,What did you do to Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.85,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I-I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:11.02,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,G-Gee, I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:13.02,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We can't go home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:18.03,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,He's far too involved in this\Nto call him an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:19.28,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Then how about this:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll allow Uesugi{**-kun} back into the home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask him to continue tutoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:29.83,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,But he'll be working alongside \Na professional tutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:33.54,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He'll be acting as her support.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:36.29,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,But we're all working so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:41.30,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Do you even suppose, if Uesugi{**-kun} was \Nbrought back in as your tutor as before,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that Yotsuba{**-kun} could earn a passing grade?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:54.35,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,From what I've seen of her grades in\Nthe second term, I have very little hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.56,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:21:00.28,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You'll only make things worse if you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.48,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:07.66,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.78,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We'll have a better chance with two tutors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:12.33,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:14.08,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Yotsuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:17.09,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-san} and the five of us can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:20.75,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I want the six of us to pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.09,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,So please, believe in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.97,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,We won't make the same mistake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.10,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,And if you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:32.18,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I would rather not say this out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've made an arrangement \Nwith an acquaintance
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,who is a board member at a high school that\Nwould allow you to enroll as third-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:43.99,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,If you fail on the next exam, \NI'll have you transfer to that school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:48.78,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,If you insist on doing things your way,\Nthe responsibility is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:50.24,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I hope you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.00,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:58.20,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I knew you would, Itsuki{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll finalize the arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:01.50,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:05.30,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We'll accept the condition that we \Ntransfer schools if we don't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:11.72,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I'm not an amenable, \Nunderstanding, intelligent child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:18.31,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It seems that the duty of a parent is to \Nhear the selfish demands of their children.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:22.57,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,And it's also the duty of a parent \Nto scold their selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.19,0:22:24.73,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,This is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:03.56,Default,Text,0,0,0,,"The Last Exam."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
